  m_text: 'Your friend''s soul got captured by a cursed doll! Block the doll''s attack
    to successfully weaken the doll and extract your friend''s soul from it!


    Remember,
    do not try to kill the doll! If you kill the doll before saving your friend,
    your friend''s soul will die too! So, becareful not to hit the doll too hard.
    If you do, you may do CPR on the doll''s chest to regain its health.


    Also,
    hitting on the body part where the soul is will damage your friend''s soul. So,
    beware to hit it softly when you see the soul near the hit area.


    For the
    final soul extraction, you must hit all body parts at the same time several times.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
